<strong>英譯版：</strong> <a href="http://scp-int.wikidot.com/scp-824-ko">http://scp-int.wikidot.com/scp-824-ko</a></p>
<hr />
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><a href="http://ko.scp-wiki.net/bangja">★</a></p>
</div>
<br />
圖片由 <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/bangja" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3064863); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3064863&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1605101191" alt="Bangja" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3064863)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/bangja" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3064863); return false;">Bangja</a></span> 製作</div>
<hr />
<div class="credit-back" style="text-align: center;">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/2" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="height:2em;width: 100%;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
